    Rigidbody Kinematic motion it''s a common complaint that motion jitters/stutters
    or is "not smooth". The key points are:


    - Tracked Target''s Rigidbody must
    have Interpolation enabled

    - Cinemachine Camera must use SmartUpdate (default)
    or LateUpdate

'
  Kind: 1
